ation/onboarding_test.go \\(570 lines\\)\n- docs/API_ONBOARDING.md \\(378 lines\\)\n- deployment/STEP_75_CHECKLIST.md \\(424 lines\\)\n\nFILES MODIFIED:\n- internal/server/server.go \\(+15 lines\\)\n  * Added OnboardingHandler initialization\n  * Registered /agent/onboard route with auth\n\nSee PHASE_11_PRD.md Step 75 and specs/committed/STEP_75_INTERROGATOR_AGENT.md\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n\\)\")"
